  "excerpt": "<p><p>It’s only the first week of October, and you probably already see a recurring theme on my blog posts: Halloween! I just can’t get enough of it! Today I’m sharing a bunch of my favorite Etsy Halloween picks. Expect more of the theme throughout the month!</p></p>",
  "content": "<p>It’s only the first week of October, and you probably already see a recurring theme on my blog posts: Halloween! I just can’t get enough of it! Today I’m sharing a bunch of my favorite Etsy Halloween picks. Expect more of the theme throughout the month!</p><p>Can you even handle how amazing some of these items are!?! I want them all! Hop over to the</p><em><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/treasury/MTAzNjM3NjF8MjcyNzg4MzAyMA/halloween-favorites\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">original treasury on Etsy</a><p>,</p></em><p>and have fun shopping from these talented artisans!</p><ol><li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/110928261/happy-halloween-banner-stamped-embossed?ref=tre-2727883020-1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Paper Etc. Studio</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/245906154/poisoned-apple-witch-spell-halloween?ref=tre-2727883020-2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Raggedy Ree</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/210151747/wide-brim-halloween-witch-hat-wizard-hat?ref=tre-2727883020-3\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">HandiCraftKate</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/98022368/zombie-headband-green-zombie-brains?ref=tre-2727883020-4\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Janine Basil</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/247622540/scare-crow-gown-halloween-costume?ref=tre-2727883020-5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Luna &#x26; Beans</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/195919884/boo-blocks-boo-wood-blocks-halloween?ref=tre-2727883020-6\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">The Posh Pear Shop</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/224239509/womens-off-shoulder-halloween-shirt-its?ref=tre-2727883020-7\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Fierce Clothing</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/109715970/wicked-witch-dictionary-art-print-wizard?ref=tre-2727883020-8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ReImagination Prints</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/204923632/halloween-bat-girl-mask-bat-costume-mask?ref=tre-2727883020-9\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Higgins Creek</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/222427648/knit-pumpkins-halloween-decor-pumpkin?ref=tre-2727883020-10\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Nevada Knits</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/204467885/crack-me-black-raven-egg-halloween?ref=tre-2727883020-11\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Little Elephant Crafts</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/205392931/pumpkin-ring-halloween-jewelry-jack-o?ref=tre-2727883020-12\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ThinkUpJewelry</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/215804624/70-denier-skeleton-bones-tights?ref=tre-2727883020-13\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Leggs Beautiful</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/109982710/12-chocolate-caramel-toffee-skulls?ref=tre-2727883020-14\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Rosebud Chocolates</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/84103202/halloween-necklace-raven-necklace-in?ref=tre-2727883020-15\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Fable and Fury</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/104671687/happy-halloween-vintage-gift-tags-set-of?ref=tre-2727883020-16\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Songbird Greetings</a></li></ol><p>Which is your favorite Halloween-y handcrafted item?</p>",
